OL,3,CStuart Hall was given infected blood
OL,4,Cwhen being treated for leukaemia in
OL,5,C1984
OL,7,FA man who was given infected blood
OL,8,Fduring treatment for leukaemia says
OL,9,Fthe government is "kicking the can
OL,10,Fdown the road" when it comes to
OL,11,Fcompensation.
OL,13,FDuring the 70s and 80s, more than
OL,14,F30,000 people in the UK were given
OL,15,Ftreatments infected with HIV and
OL,16,FHepatitis C.
OL,18,FThe final report by the government's
OL,19,Finquiry into the scandal is due to be
OL,20,Fpublished on Monday 20 May.
