OL,3,CStuart Hall was given infected blood
OL,4,Cwhen being treated for leukaemia in
OL,5,C1984
OL,7,FIn an interview with ITV Border,
OL,8,FStuart said: "I'd spent years going
OL,9,Fthrough treatment for leukaemia and
OL,10,Fthen I had ten years of regular
OL,11,Fcheckups for blood tests to make sure
OL,12,Fthat the cancer hasn't come back.
OL,14,F"And just as I was getting to the tail
OL,15,Fend of all those checks and all that
OL,16,Fmonitoring, then a letter arrived to
OL,17,Ftell me I might be infected with a
OL,18,Fvirus.
