OL,3,CStuart Hall was given infected blood
OL,4,Cwhen being treated for leukaemia in
OL,5,C1984
OL,7,F"It can lead to serious liver damage
OL,8,Fand liver cirrhosis and liver cancer
OL,9,Fand possibly death. And I lived with
OL,10,Fthat for 30 years. It takes a mental
OL,11,Ftoll. It's it's like a life sentence."
OL,13,FStuart was given a liver transplant in
OL,14,F2021 and now lives happily with his
OL,15,Fwife at home, going for regular
OL,16,Fappointments at a hospital in
OL,17,FNewcastle.
OL,19,FA government inquiry into the infected
OL,20,Fblood scandal began in 2018.
