OL,7,FA spokesperson for the UK Government
OL,8,Fsaid: "This was an appalling tragedy
OL,9,Fthat never should have happened. We
OL,10,Fare clear that justice needs to be
OL,11,Fdone, and swiftly.
OL,13,F"This includes establishing a new body
OL,14,Fto deliver an Infected Blood
OL,15,FCompensation Scheme, it will have all
OL,16,Fthe funding needed to deliver
OL,17,Fcompensation once they have identified
OL,18,Fthe victims and assessed claims.
